---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Products" description="Explore Yilong Scrubs range of premium medical uniforms. Including Elite (205GSM), Versatile (180GSM), and Air (130GSM) series.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Collection Categorization</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-20 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">Our fabric systems are engineered for the specific demands of healthcare environments.</p>
    
    <div class="space-y-32">
      <!-- 205GSM -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold rounded-full text-sm mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">The Elite Series</div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">205GSM Performance</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 italic mb-6">Heavy-duty performance meets premium comfort.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Engineered for the most demanding medical environments. Our Elite series provides maximum opacity and high abrasion resistance while maintaining 4-way stretch flexibility.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8 text-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">✓</span> Maximum Opacity
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">✓</span> Abrasion Resistant
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">✓</span> Professional Drape
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">✓</span> 4-Way Stretch
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 border-l-4 border-primary pl-4">Ideal for: Surgeons, Emergency Response teams, and high-intensity environments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 aspect-square rounded-3xl order-1 lg:order-2"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- 180GSM -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="bg-slate-100 aspect-square rounded-3xl"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-secondary/10 text-secondary font-bold rounded-full text-sm mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">The Versatile Series</div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">180GSM Standard</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 italic mb-6">The gold standard of modern medical apparel.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Designed for the everyday hero. This fabric offers an ultra-soft hand feel, superior moisture-wicking properties, and complete wrinkle resistance for a polished look all day long.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8 text-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-secondary font-bold">✓</span> Ultra-Soft Feel
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-secondary font-bold">✓</span> Moisture-Wicking
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-secondary font-bold">✓</span> Wrinkle-Resistant
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-secondary font-bold">✓</span> All-Day Comfort
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 border-l-4 border-secondary pl-4">Ideal for: General nursing, dental clinics, and everyday professional wear.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 130GSM -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 font-bold rounded-full text-sm mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">The Air Series</div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">130GSM Lightweight</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 italic mb-6">Stay cool and agile all day long.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">When the heat is on, the Air series delivers. Featuring feather-light weight and maximum breathability with quick-dry technology, it's the perfect choice for high-activity roles.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8 text-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span> Feather-Light
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span> Max Breathability
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span> Quick-Dry Tech
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span> High Mobility
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Ideal for: Pediatric care, aesthetics, and hot-climate environments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 aspect-square rounded-3xl order-1 lg:order-1"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
